node.text:
Devin Armani Booker of USA Olympic Basket Team bites the gold medal won in the Olympic final against France wearing a stainless steel Rolex GMT-Master II ‘Pepsi’. 
This watch is equipped with a bidirectional rotatable bezel and a 24-hour graduated two-colour cerachrom insert in red and blue ceramic, fitted on a jubilee bracelet ref 126710BLRO🔴🔵
⌚️tag price: $ 11,250.00

@jacobandco’s insane Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon in the crystal clear, full sapphire version 👀

A watch case made completely out of sapphire crystal is one of the top achievements in high watchmaking. The Bugatti Chiron Sapphire Crystal is the result of several months of materials processing, high level machinery and hand polishing to produce a case that exposes every part of the 578 hand-decorated and hand-assembled components of the JCAM37 manual wound caliber.
Limited to 7 pieces worldwide 
⌚️tag price: $1,300,000

node.text:
Irish MMA fighter Conor McGregor @thenotoriousmma celebrated his wife's birthday a few days ago wearing his insane @jacobandco Astronomia ‘Baguette’ tourbillon in rose gold. 
The watch features a total of 342 invisibly set baguette-cut diamonds that adorn the dial’s backdrop, while 80 invisibly set, baguette-cut diamonds make up the lugs. Its four-arm movement rotates and floats through the sapphire and diamond-bound space of the completely see-through case. Limited edition of just 18 pieces with a list price of $1,000,000.00
